org.daisy.dotify.formatter.impl.sheet

Class SheetGroupManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.daisy.dotify.formatter.impl.sheet.SheetGroupManager

  • public class SheetGroupManager
extends Object

    Provides a manager for SheetGroup.

    An EvenSizeVolumeSplitter is associated with every SheetGroup.

    Used by VolumeProvider.
